                 "[{\"text\":\"and grabbed the sword, the dirt slid off without a speck of rust on its blade. It seemed like a regular blade but light as a feather, making me wonder if the old tales about luminous treasures within the dungeons where true after all.
\"}]"
               ],
               title:"A Lumious Sword",
               author:"An unknown farmer.",
               display:{Lore:["A rare find."]}
